@startuml
title P0-B Human -> PM Intake Layer

actor Human
participant "Board API" as API
participant "Issue Route" as Route
participant "Issue Service" as Issues
participant "Protocol Service" as Protocol
participant "Retrieval + Dispatch" as Dispatch
participant "PM Agent" as PM

Human -> API : POST /companies/:companyId/intake/issues
API -> Route : validate request
Route -> Issues : create root intake issue
Issues --> Route : issue
Route -> Protocol : append ASSIGN_TASK(to PM)
Protocol --> Route : persisted protocol message
Route -> Dispatch : async brief + wake dispatch
Dispatch --> PM : PM direct-assignment wake
PM --> Protocol : REASSIGN_TASK / ASK_CLARIFICATION / ESCALATE_BLOCKER

note right of PM
No new state machine.
Reuse existing issue + protocol kernel.
end note

@enduml
